streak.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis team was just trying to win their first one,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Krikorian.\\u00c2  They are also managing challenges much more serious than any they will face in the pool.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steffens is mourning the death of her husband\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s sister, Lulu Conner, who died of what Steffens has called a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cmedical emergency\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d after traveling to Paris for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9999998160679011, \"rank\": 1.2871793876708946e-07, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}, {\"begin\": 1447, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994857349933, \"rank\": 5.142650954151497e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attacker Maddie Musselman is supporting her husband, former UCLA water polo player Patrick Woepse, as he undergoes treatment for Stage IV lung cancer.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cUnfortunately, there is been a lot of adversity outside of water polo that we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve faced,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Steffens said.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1480, \"end\": 1496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Musselman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maddie Musselman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Musselman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Musselman\"}, {\"begin\": 1554, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://